                            <comment id="17082213" author="xvanbha" created="Mon, 13 Apr 2020 10:17:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Above HiGH security alert/vulnerability is detected in our server during the nesus scan. We are using 8162 port in our application.Could you please suggest us how to fix this issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17112932" author="jbonofre" created="Thu, 21 May 2020 08:29:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t understand the issue. I tried this URL:&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8161//admin&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8161//admin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;and I got a 404 (which is correct) with ActiveMQ 5.15.13-SNAPSHOT and 5.14.5.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Can you elaborate where is the security issue here ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17112933" author="jbonofre" created="Thu, 21 May 2020 08:30:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just a note: there&apos;s no &quot;web directory&quot; in ActiveMQ console, only jsp and protected. So I don&apos;t see any issue there. Do you have an example of URL where you see a problem ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17112965" author="jbonofre" created="Thu, 21 May 2020 08:36:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Anyway, you can fully protect any URL by doing this change in &lt;tt&gt;conf/jetty.xml&lt;/tt&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&#160; &#160; &amp;lt;bean id=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;securityConstraintMapping&quot;&lt;/span&gt; class=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;org.eclipse.jetty.security.ConstraintMapping&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &amp;lt;property name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;constraint&quot;&lt;/span&gt; ref=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;securityConstraint&quot;&lt;/span&gt; /&amp;gt;
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &amp;lt;property name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;pathSpec&quot;&lt;/span&gt; value=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;/*,/api/*,/admin/*,*.jsp&quot;&lt;/span&gt; /&amp;gt;
&#160; &#160; &amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt; &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17112966" author="jbonofre" created="Thu, 21 May 2020 08:36:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m doing this change by default just in case.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17112971" author="jbonofre" created="Thu, 21 May 2020 08:43:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;See my change on&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/activemq/pull/537&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/activemq/pull/537&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think it&apos;s what you are looking for.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
